IApplication <p>Abstract base class for applications:</p> <pre><code>class IApplication {
public:
    IApplication(const Arc&lt;ServiceProvider&gt;&amp; rootServiceProvider);
    virtual ~IApplication() = default;
    Arc&lt;ServiceProvider&gt; GetRootServiceProvider() const;
    virtual void Run() = 0;
};
</code></pre> <p>The <code>IApplication</code> singleton is automatically registered when using <code>ApplicationBuilder</code>.</p>
